title: Brave New World
description: A dystopian novel by Aldous Huxley about a future society where people are engineered for specific roles.

title: Moby-Dick
description: A novel by Herman Melville about Captain Ahab's obsessive quest to kill the white whale, Moby-Dick.

title: The Odyssey
description: An epic poem by Homer, telling the story of Odysseus's journey home after the Trojan War.
